OL,6,FA cruise ship worker smuggled #2
OL,7,Fmillion worth of cocaine to UK waters
OL,8,Fbefore lowering it to two accomplices
OL,9,Fon a waiting boat. The trio have now
OL,10,Fall been jailed.
OL,12,FMilos Bigovic, from Serbia, had hidden
OL,13,Fthe 28kg of cocaine on the Marella
OL,14,FDiscovery 2 in Cartegena, Colombia,
OL,15,Fbefore the liner's Caribbean voyage
OL,16,Fwas abandoned in March 2020 as the
OL,17,FCovid-19 pandemic hit.
OL,19,FThe passengers disembarked and the
OL,20,Fship returned to Europe, where it
OL,21,Fmoored off the Isle of Wight.
