OL,6,FIt was on 25 April 2020, that Bigovic
OL,7,Fdragged the holdall containing the
OL,8,Fdrugs from his cabin to a port-side
OL,9,Fdeck and attached a rope to it.
OL,11,FHe lowered it down to his accomplices,
OL,12,FBenn Bath, 36, and Joshua Paige, 31,
OL,13,Fwho were waiting in a rigid-hulled
OL,14,Finflatable boat (Rhib) below,
OL,15,Faccording to the National Crime Agency
OL,16,F(NCA).
OL,18,FAn NCA spokesman said: "The drugs,
OL,19,Fwhich were smuggled on to the cruise
OL,20,Fship, were so heavy the rope burned
OL,21,Fthe skin from Bigovic's hand.
