OL,6,F"Bath and Paige were experienced
OL,7,Fseamen who worked in the maritime
OL,8,Findustry."
OL,10,FTheir movements were being observed by
OL,11,FNCA officers.
OL,13,FThe spokesman continued: "In the
OL,14,Fpreceding days, they had sailed Bath's
OL,15,Fown boat, the Chatham Albatross, from
OL,16,Fthe River Medway in Kent to the Isle
OL,17,Fof Wight.
