OL,6,F"They had bought the Rhib for #5,000
OL,7,Fand towed it from the Albatross so
OL,8,Fthey could get close to the Marella
OL,9,Fand accept the drugs under cover of
OL,10,Fdarkness.
OL,12,F"The 28kg of cocaine was originally
OL,13,Fsupposed to be smuggled ashore
OL,14,Fsomewhere in Europe.
OL,16,F"But when the Marella Discovery
OL,17,Fchanged course because of lockdown,
OL,18,Fthe organised crime group (OCG) behind
OL,19,Fthe drugs had to change their plans."
