OL,6,FBigovic, of Pozarevac, near Belgrade,
OL,7,Fwas jailed for 11 years in 2021 having
OL,8,Fadmitted importing cocaine.
OL,10,FBath from Staplehurst, Kent, was
OL,11,Fsentenced to 18 years and Paige from
OL,12,FHigh Halstow, Kent, to eight years
OL,13,Fafter being convicted at Winchester
OL,14,FCrown Court of the same charge.
OL,16,FNCA investigators then uncovered a
OL,17,Fsecond conspiracy involving Bath to
OL,18,Fimport another 90kg of cocaine into
OL,19,Fthe UK onboard a barge from Rotterdam
OL,20,Fin the Netherlands.
